{"tid":431499,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"西國：一旦加泰宣布獨立 就逮捕自治區主席","createTime":"2017-10-10T18:21:51.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-10T18:33:38.000Z","uid":62257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"8822b4045b81719f319614b2a062766995b94f6a","tid":431499,"uid":62257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-10T18:21:51.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://udn.com/news/story/11532/2749603\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fudn.com%2Fnews%2Fstory%2F11532%2F2749603&d=mfPxnBQwWwimlPZLDR7bY5Uc5Mn1qk%2F8nAzLhrzJJK4%3D&h=86956818\" target=\"_blank\">https://udn.com/news/story/11532/2749603</a><br />\n2017-10-11 00:46<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n彭博資訊報導，西班牙警方10日已做好準備，若加泰隆尼亞自治區政府主席普伊格蒙特（Carles Puigdemont）當天在議會片面宣布獨立，將立即加以逮捕。<br />\n<br />\n普伊格蒙特預料將在自治區議會的臨時會議上，宣布1日舉行的獨立公投結果。一旦他宣布獨立，加泰隆尼亞可能面臨馬德里當局的嚴厲懲罰、經濟崩潰的威脅，以及國際孤立等風險。<br />\n<br />\n知情人士說，西班牙國家警察局已在加泰隆尼亞部署菁英警力，隨時可採取突擊行動，但如果普伊格蒙特的聲明並未表示立即獨立，警方可能按兵不動。"},{"pid":"83d0b184cb5efe741310976ccb90d0a35403dd7f","tid":431499,"uid":62257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-10T18:27:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a8b6135798bfe30ea819c1ff81c3ac92d83b3f1b","tid":431499,"uid":62257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-10T18:33:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}